<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>NEVER SAY GOOD-BYE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw In nuoma kituok khawmte,
 Kikhen kit ta puon tiu;
 Ziechun mitin kituok hitiu,
 Kikhen kit talo di'n.

[V2]
 Kikhen kit ta puoi tiu,
 Van khela zie gam nuom achun;
 Kikhen kit ta puoi tiu.

[V3]
 2. Sepgim leh buoina khela khun,
 Kikhen kit ta puoi tiu;
 Lei ah kapin kikhen mahleng,
 Vanah kikhen umlo.

[V4]
 3. Tatsate laka I tel tieng,
 Kikhen kit ta puoi tiu;
 Kumsawt in chawihat la sai tiu,
 Kikhen kit ta puoi tiu.

[V5]
 4. Luigal gam hawih muonna munah,
 Kikhen kit ta puoi tiu;
 Krista tawh kumkhuon cheng tai tiu,
 Kikhen kitta ta lo di'n.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>409</hymn_number>
</song>